Getting and Cleaning Data - Course Project

The The R script, run_analysis.R works on two functions 
1) file
2) Process

File :
This function first check the availibilty of data, if it is not present, it downloads it and then unzip it

Process :
This fuction is based on few steps
-> Extraction : This extracts all the datasets (activity, feature, training and test)
-> Mean and Standard deviation: Load the data which concerns the mean and sd column
->Merging: Thos involves the merging of two datasets
->Resultant: Creates a Tidy dataset (Result.txt)
